    "description": "NVSHMEM is a parallel programming interface based on OpenSHMEM that\nprovides efficient and scalable communication for NVIDIA GPU clusters.\nNVSHMEM creates a global address space for data that spans the memory of\nmultiple GPUs and can be accessed with fine-grained GPU-initiated\noperations, CPU-initiated operations, and operations on CUDA streams.\n",
